title: Why Don't It Sink In?
lyrics:
Ain't it apparent?
Ain't it obvious?
Ain't it visible enough?
Ain't it crystal clear?
Why don't, why don't

Why don't, why don't, why don't it sink in?

To your head sprouting from you

In denial, all hands up in agreement

Why don't, why don't, why don't, why don't, why don't, why don't, why don't it sink in?



Why?
